fields.title: Does it always rain in London?
fields.content: They say it always rains in London and it is true! I went to london a couple of times and most of them the skies were cloudy and rain was present including the time I went to london for DeveloperDay22.

fields.title: Dublin is beautiful!
fields.content: Have you ever been to Dublin? it is beautiful specially during summer. I could experience the city first hand when I went to my first EuroPython.

fields.title: Salt Lake City has no Oxygen
fields.content:
